Hi Leendra,

I'll make a less specific claim that we _know_ is true, and maybe 
you will be able to take the solution from there.  The product of an 
even number and a natural number is always even (can you see why?).  
Does this help?  If you need another hint, write back, and I'll help 
you out! 

